body: Babalu and Uncommon Sense blog about Sara Martha Fonseca, whose "home was attacked last night...in reaction to the mass protest in Cuba scheduled for February 23, 2011, in commemoration of the murder of prisoner of conscience Orlando Zapata Tamayo."
